<!DOCTYPE html
    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>3. GST Declaration</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-indent: 0;
        }

        .s1 {
            color: black;
            font-family: "Baskerville Old Face", serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 24pt;
        }

        .s2 {
            color: black;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 13pt;
        }

        .s4 {
            color: black;
            font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        p {
            color: black;
            font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 11pt;
            margin: 0pt;
        }

        .s5 {
            color: black;
            font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <p class="s1" style="padding-left: 78pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 27pt;text-align: center;"><span>
            <%=name%>
        </span></p>
    <p class="s2" style="padding-left: 78pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 15pt;text-align: center;">
        <%=regd_address%>
    </p>
    <p class="s4" style="padding-left: 78pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;">CIN: <span>
            <%=cin%>
        </span> | Contact: <span>
            <%=contact_number%>
        </span> | E-mail: <span>
            <%=email%>
        </span> Website: <span>
            <%=website%>
        </span></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 4pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 13pt;text-align: center;">
        ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    </p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Date: <span>
            <%=date_of_application%>
        </span></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">To,</p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">The Managing Director</p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">National Securities Depository Limited</p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">4th floor, Trade World, A Wing Kamala
        Mills Compound, Senapati Bapat Marg,</p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Lower Parel, Mumbai - 400 013</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 78pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;">Subject: Declaration for not
        having GST</p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 4pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;">Dear Sir,</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">This is in connection with our
        application for admitting our securities on National Securities Depository Limited (NSDL) to enable our
        shareholders to hold their shares in dematerialised form.</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: justify;">We hereby undertake that the
        provisions regarding registration under CGST Act and SGST Act are not applicable to our company as the turnover
        is below the specified threshold limit. Therefore, the company has not applied for GST.</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p class="s5" style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Yours faithfully,</p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">For, <span>
            <%=name%>
        </span></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br /></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">(Signature)</p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Name : <span>
            <%=authorized_name%>
        </span></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"> Designation <span>
            <%=authorized_destination%>
        </span></p>
    <p style="padding-left: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">DIN:<span>
            <%=authorized_din%>
        </span>p>
</body>

</html>